Achievements.Name: Starting Boost
Achievements.Description: Change from the stopping position to accelerating position on the word "GO!".

Achievements.Name: Item Attack
Achievements.Description: Stomp your front foot when you have an item.

Achievements.Name: T Glider
Achievements.Description: Spread your arms wide to the left and right while in the air.

Achievements.Name: Landing Boost
Achievements.Description: Perform an air trick and stick the landing.

Achievements.Name: Triple Air Trick
Achievements.Description: Twist your body while in the air and perform at least 3 air tricks.

Achievements.Name: Front Grab
Achievements.Description: Raise your front leg while in the air and perform a front grab.

Achievements.Name: Side Grab
Achievements.Description: Raise your back leg while in the air and perform a back grab.

Achievements.Name: Air Trick Sideway Combo
Achievements.Description: Perform an air trick with 2 consecutive horizontal revolutions and land.

Achievements.Name: Air Trick Vertical Combo
Achievements.Description: Perform an air trick with 2 consecutive vertical revolutions and land.

Achievements.Name: Boost Max
Achievements.Description: Make a clean landing with your boost at max.

Achievements.Name: Riding Trials Complete
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Riding Trials.

Achievements.Name: Fly Distance Trials Complete
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Fly Distance Trials.

Achievements.Name: Air Trick Trials Complete
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Air Trick Trials.

Achievements.Name: Jib Trick Trials Complete
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Jib Trick Trials.

Achievements.Name: Free Race Master
Achievements.Description: Finish a "Free Race" race with Rank A.

Achievements.Name: Downhill Slalom Master
Achievements.Description: Finish a "Downhill Slalom" race with Rank A.

Achievements.Name: Balloon Buster Master
Achievements.Description: Finish a "Balloon Buster" race with Rank A.

Achievements.Name: Fly Distance Master
Achievements.Description: Finish a "Fly Distance" race with Rank A.

Achievements.Name: Trick Score Master
Achievements.Description: Finish a "Trick Score" race with Rank A.

Achievements.Name: No Crash Ace
Achievements.Description: Finish a race in 1st place without crashing.

Achievements.Name: Star Trick
Achievements.Description: Get a star in a race while performing an air trick.

Achievements.Name: I Can Fly!
Achievements.Description: Get big air in a race.

Achievements.Name: Jib & Switch
Achievements.Description: Perform a switch riding while jibbing.

Achievements.Name: Only One Winner
Achievements.Description: Win a multiplayer challenge.

Achievements.Name: Intense Rivalry
Achievements.Description: Crash hard into another player.

Achievements.Name: One-Two Finish
Achievements.Description: Finish a race in 1st and 2nd place with a friend.

Achievements.Name: World Debut
Achievements.Description: Get your score registered in the world rankings.

Achievements.Name: EZ Jump
Achievements.Description: Jump while you are boarding.
